title: RealMan Robotics launches three joint modules for robotics
description:
RealMan said its servo joints deliver high torque density, fast dynamic response, high precision, reliability, and cost efficiency.

The post RealMan Robotics launches three joint modules for robotics appeared first on The Robot Report.
